<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY: 

This notice announces the annual adjustments to the national average payment rates for meals served in child care,
outside-school-hours care and adult day care centers, the food service payment rates for meals served in day care
homes, and the administrative reimbursement rates for sponsors of day care homes to reflect changes in the Consumer
Price Index. Further adjustments are made to these rates to reflect the higher costs of providing meals in the States
of Alaska and Hawaii. The adjustments contained in this notice are required by the statutes and regulations governing
the Child and Adult Care Food Program (CACFP).



