adverse environmental effects identified in the FEIS will be minimized or avoided by incorporating mitigative measures
as conditions of Federal funding approval and permit issuance. These measures are described in Section 4.0 of the
FEIS.
(4) A wetland mitigation plan providing in-kind and on-site replacement for unavoidable adverse impacts to existing
wetlands has been developed and will be implemented, resulting in no net loss of wetland habitat values over time.
